# ==================================================================
# Troubleshooting
# ==================================================================
# - psycopg2 install fails -> use psycopg2-binary instead (already included above)
# - ipykernel error in notebook -> pip install ipykernel (inside venv)
# - openpyxl missing error on Excel read/write -> pip install openpyxl
# - .env variables not loading -> confirm load_dotenv() called before os.getenv()
# - DB connection refused -> check port matches your actual PostgreSQL instance (5433/5434)
